#. type: Plain text
#: _docs/Build_Metadata_Reference.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "    If `UpdateCheckMode` is set to `HTTP`, a pattern should be added\n"
#| "    after the `Version`. The pattern is used to generate a value\n"
