msgid "F-Droid Limited controls many potential phishing domains like [fdroid.org](https://whois.icann.org/lookup?name=fdroid.org), [f-droid.com](https://whois.icann.org/lookup?name=f-droid.com), and [f-dro1d.org](https://whois.icann.org/lookup?name=f-dro1d.org). (donations of more are welcome!)"
msgstr "F-Droid Limited überwacht viele potentielle Phishing-Domains, wie [fdroid.org](https://whois.icann.org/lookup?name=fdroid.org), [f-droid.com](https://whois.icann.org/lookup?name=f-droid.com) und [f-dro1d.org](https://whois.icann.org/lookup?name=f-dro1d.org). (die Bekanntgabe weiterer wird begrüßt!)"

